Islamabad - wani rahoto na amurka ya ce sama da'yan pakistan 6,000 ne ke boye a afghanistan, yawancinsu'yan kungiyar taliban ne da ke da alhakin kai hari kan sojojin pakistan da fararen hula.
Rahoton da kungiyar ta fitar a wannan makon ya ce kungiyar da a turance ake kira da (-e-), (ttp), na da alaka da kungiyar'yan uwa musulmi ta kasar afghanistan.
Wasu daga cikin'yan kabilar ttp har sun shiga kungiyar is, wacce keda hedikwata a gabashin afghanistan.
Gwamnatin afghanistan ba ta mayar da martani ba a ranar lahadi kan bukatar da kamfanin associated press ya nema.
Rahoton ya ce a afghanistan, kungiyar taliban da aka fi sani da is a lardin khorasan, ta sha kashi a hannun jami'an tsaron afghanistan da amurka da kuma kungiyar tsaro ta nato, har ma a wani lokaci ta na fatattakar'yan taliban na afghanistan.
Kungiyar sa ido kan'yan ta'adda ta amurka ce ta shirya rahoton, wanda ke bibiyar kungiyoyin ta'addanci a duniya.
Rahoton ya kiyasta cewa membobin kungiyar is a afghanistan sun kai 2,200, kuma yayin da shugabanta ya yi juyin mulki, har yanzu ana kirga su a cikin shugabanninta na kasa mai suna mohammad al- national.
Rahoton ya kuma ce, kungiyar sa ido ta samu bayanai cewa manyan shugabannin kasashen musulmi biyu, abu▁qutaibah da kuma abu hajar al--, a kwanan nan sun isa afghanistan daga gabas ta tsakiya.
